description: Plain wooden walls rise from a buffed cherrywood floor.  Just above a worn rug hangs a decorative linden branch wreath, and a paneled haon ceiling completes the picture.  A wide faenor-trimmed table and a gold-trimmed ebonwood chest stand side by side in the middle of the room.
